OL,3,E"DESMONDG``````````````````````````````
OL,5, When I get up in the morning, I switch 
OL,6, on the TV, flick to Channel 4 and put  
OL,7, on Digi. I'm all excited and go        
OL,8, straight to the letters page. (not just
OL,9, to see latest "The Man" story).        
OL,11, The letters appear and I laugh at the  
OL,12, funnies and swear at the bad ones. Then
OL,13, I notice mine is not there, not again I
OL,14, cry. Why....                           
OL,15,BIanos@globalnet.co.uk                  
OL,17,FS'okay, man. It's just because we hate 
OL,18,Fyou.                                   
