OL,5, The last place I would ever want to go 
OL,6, is the "Newsgroups". I understand      
OL,7, Digitiser wants to set up a group all  
OL,8, of its own. That's up to you, but I    
OL,9, wouldn't bother.                       
OL,11, You can expect what it will be like -  
OL,12, loads of Amiga users with nothing left 
OL,13, to do but whine on the Net, idiots     
OL,14, spewing vitriol amongst themselves,    
OL,15, porno and advertisements.B             
