OL,3,EOLLIEG`````````````````````````````````
OL,5, People who write in saying "I completed
OL,6, Lylat wars in one hour", or some other 
OL,7, game in a ridiculous time, are complete
OL,8, idiots.                                
OL,10, So they claim to have got all the      
OL,11, medals, activated sound test, seen the 
OL,12, new title screen and the two extra     
OL,13, endings on expert mode. The TRUE       
OL,14, challenge in a game is seeing all the  
OL,15, secrets the game has to offer.         
OL,16,BMs0u5018@Liverpool.ac.uk               
OL,18,FYes - and then you can smash it up!    
