OL,3,ENICK"G`````````````````````````````````
OL,5, Species: Puffius Jacketus.             
OL,6, Distiguishing features: Characterised  
OL,7, by shiny puffy plumage and large       
OL,8, trainers, some variants wear shades.   
OL,10, Can be located by following its call of
OL,11, "Yeah man, sorted" or Kickin' tunes    
OL,12, bro'". Likes to "hang" with other Puffy
OL,13, Jackets and "chill" to "Wicked Tunez". 
OL,14, Evidence suggests this plague is       
OL,15, spreading fast. There is even one      
OL,16, living next to me at Uni.              
OL,17,BD.J.Illingworth@hist.hull.ac.uk        
OL,19,FYou ought to strangle it.              
